official_title: The Femscope Calm Collect Device to Obtain Cervical Cells for Cancer Screening
inclusion_criteria:
- Healthy female ages 21-45 with female reproductive organs present at the time of study.
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
Must have maximum age of 45 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Pregnancy
* Menopausal
* Age less than 21 years
* Age of 46+ years
* History of reproductive cancer
* Hysterectomy
